*.sublime-workspace

# ============================================================================
# Claude Code Configuration (Allow skills to be committed)
# ============================================================================
# Global gitignore blocks .claude/, but we want skills shared with team
!.claude/
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/skills/**/*.md
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/hooks/*.sh
!.claude/CLAUDE.md

